Package org.forgerock.openam.notifications

Interface Subscription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    public interface Subscription
extends AutoCloseable
    Represents a single consumer of events.

    A subscription may be over multiple topics.

    A subscription is closable. Once a subscription is closed, it will not receive any more notifications.

    Since:
    14.0.0
